we are going to build a platform that will serve as a marketplace for solar energy:

the intitial journey will be where user registers, gives his address details, typical monthly bill, size of the roof and/or terrrace for installation 
there will be an integration with google maps, nasa api, for understanding the solar potential of the location
based on that we will provide a set of recommendations of how much KW user will need to install, is it recommended to have battery backup or not
then we will go into each of the modules below for further stages of the journey:

it will have 4 tabs and 4 modules totally 

module 1: Simplification of finance for someone that has decided to install solar but is unsure of the costing
    we will have a journey for how much KW they want 
        with battery 
        without battery 
        what will it cost as variations 
        how much will it cost per month for the end users
    1.1: how will we pay the installer 
    1.2: how will we pay the financier 
    1.3: how will we pay ourselves -- admin persona only 

module 2: Marketplace of solar 
    installers: this will have list of all installers in the pin provided 
    equipment suppliers: this will have the list of all suppliers that will be a good fit for given location 
    architects and consultants: this will have the list of all architects/consultants who can provide expertise here 

module 3: Dashboard and mobile app for monitoring 
        users: will be able to monitor if their installations are ok 
        service providers: solarmoms who will service the installations 
        service packages: annual packages for maintenance

module 4: Carbon credits and resale marketplace 
        users: will be able to see how much carbon credits they have generated 
        resale: will be able to resell the carbon credits on a marketplace we will build for this purpose 
        admin: will be able to monitor the carbon credit generation and resale marketplace
